data.description: New price 12-4-23!  Diamond in the rough!  4 Bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 3 car garage, inside utility, and storm shelter!  This home has granite counters in kitchen and bathrooms, entry to back yard from dining area, open kitchen design, large living room, secondary bedrooms are good sized as well.  You will want to see this one!  It just might be the one you have been looking for.  This property may qualify for Seller Financing (Vendee).  Buyer to verify details.
